( Pen-to-drill offset: the X/Y values below come from the calibration )
( procedure in README.md and are specific to the current holder setup. )
(MSG, Resetting tool coordinates to current position.)
M0      (Moving to drilling position.)
G04 P0 ( dwell for no time -- G64 should not smooth over this point )
G00 X36.80 Y16.90 Z10

(MSG, Resetting tool coordinates to current position.)
M0      (Adjust Z position.)
G92 X0 Y0 Z0
